01:01:48.430 --> 01:01:50.310
You silly girl.

01:01:53.500 --> 01:01:57.210
Turn off the radio if
you can't concentrate.

01:01:57.310 --> 01:01:58.410
That's okay.

01:02:06.450 --> 01:02:08.260
