01:02:25.470 --> 01:02:27.750
My baby is nagging me.

01:02:39.750 --> 01:02:44.600
Why are you using
so much of it?

01:02:45.320 --> 01:02:47.330
A small amount
doesn't work.

01:02:55.200 --> 01:02:55.800
Wow...

01:02:57.340 --> 01:02:59.870
