01:16:08.890 --> 01:16:11.570
<i>Please look after
my grandmother.</i>

01:16:12.760 --> 01:16:14.170
<i>I'm sorry.</i>

01:16:14.800 --> 01:16:17.240
<i>Also, thank you.</i>

01:16:19.800 --> 01:16:20.800
<i>Mr. Lee...</i>

01:16:23.340 --> 01:16:30.620
<i>The light still feels
strange to me.</i>

