Hye-ji is dead.

01:22:06.920 --> 01:22:08.360
Hye-ji...

01:22:09.920 --> 01:22:12.830
I miss grandma.

01:22:12.890 --> 01:22:15.800
Take me back to her.

01:22:16.390 --> 01:22:18.770
I told you to stop
mentioning her!

01:22:18.830 --> 01:22:20.140
Why do you keep doing it?

01:22:23.630 --> 01:22:25.640
